<HEAD>Reagans To Celebrate First Lady's Birthday By Seeing `Les
Miserables'</HEAD>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   President Reagan and his wife Nancy plan to
celebrate the first lady's birthday today by attending a
performance of ``Les Miserables'' at the Kennedy Center Opera
House, according to a White House announcement.
   Asked on Tuesday which birthday the first couple was
celebrating, spokesman Marlin Fitzwater replied with a grin, ``The
