   _ ``The O'Neill Plays,'' Jason Robards and Colleen Dewhurst star
in revivals of Eugene O'Neill's ``Long Day's Journey Into Night''
and ``Ah, Wilderness!'' The plays are performed in repertory. Check
theater for playing schedule. Neil Simon, 757-8646. Teletron.
Available.
   _ ``The Night of the Iguana,'' a revival of the Tennessee
