by top executives of the company is proposing to acquire it for
$7.50 a share.
   Scientific-Atlanta rose } to 15\. The company said it knew of no
reason for the increase in the stock price.
   Incstar, traded on the American Stock Exchange, climbed 1} to
8[. The company raised its earnings projection for the fiscal year
that ends next March.
   As measured by Wilshire Associates' index of more than 5,000
actively traded stocks, the market lost $28.67 billion, or 1.04
percent, in value.
   The NYSE's composite index of all its listed common stocks
dropped 1.81 to 153.76.
